The Peoples Democratic Party Governors Forum (PDP-GF) has congratulated the candidate of the party in November 16, 2019, Bayelsa state gubernatorial election, Senator Diri Duoye, on his declaration as the governor-elect. A statement issued by the Director-General of the Forum, Hon CID Maduabum, in Abuja on Thursday also congratulated Senator Lawrence Ewhruojakpo who has now emerged as the deputy governor-elect of Bayelsa State. ALSO READ: Reps demand records on CBN revenues, capital projects Fulfill Oyo 2019 coalition agreements, ADC candidates charge… Proscribed NURTW leaders warn Oyo govt against introduction… Reps demand records on CBN revenues, capital projects Beyelsa Supreme Court judgement: Warn Oshiomhle to stop… The statement observed that their victory at the Supreme Court was all the more remarkable as it reaffirmed “the fact that God is in charge of the affairs of men. It shows that the truth and the peoples will ultimately triumph. This is a great victory for democracy and the rule of law.” The statement welcomed Duoye to the PDP Governors’ Forum, praying that God should give him the wisdom and strength to steer the ship of Bayelsa State aright. The forum implored him to carry everyone along and run an inclusive government worthy of the ideals of the PDP governors’ family. SHOCKING LIFE STORY!!! Abuja Man reveals (FREE) secret Fruits that Increased his Manh0d size and Lasting Power in just 7days… CLICK HERE TO GET IT!!! STAY STRONGER, LONGER AND SATISFY MADAM LIKE NEVER BEFORE WITH THIS NATURAL SUPPLEMENTS WITH NO SIDE EFFECTS. CLICK NOW. CLICK HERE NOW TO WORK FROM HOME ENTIRELY AT YOUR OWN CONVINIENCE AND GET PAID WEEKLY, DIRECTLY INTO YOUR SPECIFIED BANK ACCOUNT.REGISTRATION IS ABSOLUTELY FREE.